âš ï¸ Common Issues & Fixes
Problem	Solution
java.net.BindException: Address already in use	Port 5000 is already used. Try another port, e.g., 5050.
java.net.ConnectException: Connection refused	Make sure the server is started before the client.
java.io.IOException: Connection reset	Ensure both programs close sockets properly.
Firewall blocks connection	Temporarily disable firewall or allow Java network access.

